track_notes: This is a GPS track walked in September 2009. Leave the rear of the Patterdale Hotel by the path. Climb Thornhow End to Birks (Wainwright LDW-125). Continue to St Sunday Crag LD-010. Traverse Cofa Pike to Fairfield LD-008 then continue to Hart Crag (LDW-027). Leave the ridge to make for Hartsop-Above-How (LDW-137). Now easy downhill back to the A592 Kirkstone Pass and Patterdale.
track_title: St Sunday Crag Fairfield and 3 Wainwrights
